    "title": "UPS India International Enterprises is Hiring: Warehouse Manager (Principal)",
    "description": "Are you a skilled Warehouse Manager looking for your next big career move? UPS India International Enterprises in Jodhpur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout UPS India International Enterprises:\nUPS India International Enterprises is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with warehousing teams for inbound and outbound operations\n• Optimize delivery routes to reduce cost and improve efficiency\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Conduct periodic vendor audits and evaluate logistics partners\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBA from a recognized university\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Route Optimization\n• Proficiency in TMS\n• Proficiency in WMS\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with UPS India International Enterprises!",
